  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/910280/extras/1f1376512ec0ffe3bf1e3a08784a97c0.avif?t=1753376481\" width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Maze Running!</strong>     Your hero must make their way through a maze with the objective of reaching the end, while avoiding enemies. The level will reset if the enemies catch you. Traverse through the island unlocking over 50 levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Game Modes!</strong>     Some levels will be timed, require you to activate switches, and even collect purple pysankas scattered throughout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pysanka Challenge!</strong>     Run around collecting Pysankas (Little Eggs) while keeping your head up for enemies on your tail.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Keep It Simple!</strong>     Learn how to play in 15 seconds. No exhausting tutorials, no in-game purchases, just fast and fluid gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/910280/extras/1f1376512ec0ffe3bf1e3a08784a97c0.avif?t=1753376481\" width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Maze Running!</strong>     Your hero must make their way through a maze with the objective of reaching the end, while avoiding enemies. The level will reset if the enemies catch you. Traverse through the island unlocking over 50 levels! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Game Modes!</strong>     Some levels will be timed, require you to activate switches, and even collect purple pysankas scattered throughout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pysanka Challenge!</strong>     Run around collecting Pysankas (Little Eggs) while keeping your head up for enemies on your tail.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Keep It Simple!</strong>     Learn how to play in 15 seconds. No exhausting tutorials, no in-game purchases, just fast and fluid gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
